        "plaintext": "Complete Ritou Escape Plan",
        "markdown": "Complete \u25c0Ritou Escape Plan\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Ritou_Escape_Plan\u25b7"
    },
    "rewards": null,
    "steps": [
        {
            "tag": "ol",
            "steps": [
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Use the power of \u25c0Electro\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Electro\u25b7 on the \u25c0Sky Kitsune Statue\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Sky_Kitsune_Statue\u25b7"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Obtain the <img:ward_(a_strange_story_in_konda)> \u25c0ward\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Ward_(A_Strange_Story_in_Konda)\u25b7",
                    "img": {
                        "ward_(a_strange_story_in_konda)": "Item_Ward.png"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Go to \u25c0Konda Village\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Konda_Village\u25b7"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Ask the locals for information"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "ul",
                    "steps": [
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "This step is completed after talking to Futaba, Takeru, and Saimon Eri."
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "tag": "ul",
                    "steps": [
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "\u25c0Futaba\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Futaba\u25b7 is by the gully near the village chief"
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "\u25c0Takeru\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Takeru\u25b7 is on the rooftop of a house by the stream on the south-eastern edge of the village"
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "\u25c0Saimon Eri\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Saimon_Eri\u25b7 is standing near some fruit vines next to a shrine on the road leading north out of the village"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Ask the Konda Village \u25c0Chief\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Konda_Densuke\u25b7 for information"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "ul",
                    "steps": [
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "This step does not appear if Konda Densuke was spoken to during the previous step."
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Look for clues 0/3"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "ul",
                    "steps": [
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "Obtain <img:cargo_bag_fished_out_from_water> \u25c0Cargo Bag Fished Out From Water\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Cargo_Bag_Fished_Out_From_Water\u25b7 from the bags washed down the gully southeast (obtainable after speaking to Futaba)",
                            "img": {
                                "cargo_bag_fished_out_from_water": "Item_Sack.png"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "Defeat enemies and obtain <img:ragged_list_of_goods> \u25c0Ragged List of Goods\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Ragged_List_of_Goods\u25b7 from the cart outside of Konda Village's northeast entrance by the river",
                            "img": {
                                "ragged_list_of_goods": "Book_Thank-You_Letter.png"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "Obtain <img:purse_by_the_dried-up_well> \u25c0Purse by the Dried-Up Well\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Purse_by_the_Dried-Up_Well\u25b7 from the bucket behind the Konda well",
                            "img": {
                                "purse_by_the_dried-up_well": "Item_Bag_of_Mora.png"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "tag": "ul",
                    "steps": [
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "<img:hilichurl> \u25c0Hilichurl\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Hilichurl\u25b7 \u00d72",
                            "img": {
                                "hilichurl": "Hilichurl_Icon.png"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "<img:wooden_shield_hilichurl_guard> \u25c0Wooden Shield Hilichurl Guard\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Wooden_Shield_Hilichurl_Guard\u25b7 \u00d71",
                            "img": {
                                "wooden_shield_hilichurl_guard": "Hilichurl_Icon.png"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Cut a deal with the Village Chief"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Look for the Chief's diary on the rooftop"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Head over to the designated area recorded in the notebook"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "ul",
                    "steps": [
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "Defeat the enemies and obtain the \u25c0Old Key\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Old_Key\u25b7"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "tag": "ul",
                    "steps": [
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "<img:nobushi_jintouban> \u25c0Nobushi: Jintouban\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Nobushi:_Jintouban\u25b7 \u00d71",
                            "img": {
                                "nobushi_jintouban": "Nobushi_Jintouban_Icon.png"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "<img:nobushi_hitsukeban> \u25c0Nobushi: Hitsukeban\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Nobushi:_Hitsukeban\u25b7 \u00d71",
                            "img": {
                                "nobushi_hitsukeban": "Nobushi_Hitsukeban_Icon.png"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "<img:treasure_hoarders_hydro_potioneer> \u25c0Treasure Hoarders: Hydro Potioneer\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Treasure_Hoarders:_Hydro_Potioneer\u25b7 \u00d71",
                            "img": {
                                "treasure_hoarders_hydro_potioneer": "Treasure_Hoarder_Hydro_Potioneer_Icon.png"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "<img:treasure_hoarders_pyro_potioneer> \u25c0Treasure Hoarders: Pyro Potioneer\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Treasure_Hoarders:_Pyro_Potioneer\u25b7 \u00d71",
                            "img": {
                                "treasure_hoarders_pyro_potioneer": "Treasure_Hoarder_Pyro_Potioneer_Icon.png"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "tag": "li",
                            "text": "<img:treasure_hoarders_scout> \u25c0Treasure Hoarders: Scout\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Treasure_Hoarders:_Scout\u25b7 \u00d71",
                            "img": {
                                "treasure_hoarders_scout": "Treasure_Hoarder_Scout_1_Icon.png"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Descend into the well in Konda Village"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Explore the bottom of the well"
                },
                {
                    "tag": "li",
                    "text": "Talk to \u25c0Hanachirusato\u25b6\u25c1https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Hanachirusato\u25b7"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
